    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "UNITED S GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "DATE: October 5, 1959",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "FROM",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "SUBJECT: UNIDENTIFIED FLYING OBJECTS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "(FLYING SAUCERS)",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Lemo 10-13-58 pointed out",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "that our policy concerning unidentified flying objects",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "(flying saucers) is to conduct no investigation but",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "immediately refer facts to the Air Force (Bureau Bulletin",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "Number 57, 10-1-47); that SAC Letter Number 38, 3-25-49,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "reiterated this policy and set out data desired by Air Force",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "to be obtained when complaint received; that SAC Letter",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Number 83, 8-29-52, again pointed out our policy; that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Air Force, as late as 11-12-57, assured Bureau would be advised",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "of any developments in this field of interest to us; and that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "there appeared to be no necessity for further instructions",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "to field or insertion in Agents' Handbook or Manual of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "instructions of our policy relating to flying saucers.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "During past 12 months no complaints regarding",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "flying saucers have been referred to Bureau. During this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "period we have received two inquiries regarding this alleged",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "[unclear] and on both occasions the person making the inquiry",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "been referred to OSI.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "your information. At this time there appears",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "ity for additional instructions for the field",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
